  e.Environment Variables (KRaft Core)
CLUSTER_ID
Kafka cluster needs a unique ID
Why needed?
All brokers must belong to same cluster
If mismatch → cluster will not form ❌
👉 Simple explanation:
CLUSTER_ID ensures all Kafka brokers are part of the same cluster.

KAFKA_CONTROLLER_QUORUM_VOTERS
Kafka needs to know:
👉 Which brokers act as controllers
This tells Kafka which brokers will manage cluster metadata and leader election.

