Health Checks ----kafka-broker-api-versions.sh
Why Your Setup Uses This for Health Checks
From your StatefulSet:
Liveness:
kafka-broker-api-versions.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
“Is Kafka still alive?” If ❌ fails: Kubernetes restarts the pod
Readiness:
kafka-broker-api-versions.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
“Is Kafka ready to accept traffic?” If ❌ fails: Traffic is NOT sent to this pod



